    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "This can be done with the `TASK_NODE_CREATE_SERVER` subtask:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nconst taskNames = require(\"hardhat/builtin-tasks/task-names\");\r\n\r\nasync function main() {\r\n  const server = await hre.run(taskNames.TASK_NODE_CREATE_SERVER, {\r\n    hostname: \"localhost\",\r\n    port: 8545,\r\n    provider: hre.network.provider\r\n  });\r\n\r\n  await server.listen();\r\n\r\n  await server.waitUntilClosed();\r\n}\r\n\r\nmain()\r\n  .then(() => process.exit(0))\r\n  .catch(error => {\r\n    console.error(error);\r\n    process.exit(1);\r\n  });\r\n```",
